<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>At Our Flower Shop, we take your privacy seriously and are committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect about you and how we use it.</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We may collect certain information or data about you when you use our site. This includes:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Your contact details such as name, email address, postal address, and telephone number, as entered in our contact form or checkout page.</li>
    <li>Your IP address, and details of which version of web browser you used and information on how you use the site.</li>
    <li>Data that can be collected using cookies. Please see our Cookie Policy for more details.</li>
</ul>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>We use your information to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Process your orders and provide you with services.</li>
    <li>Improve the content and design of the website.</li>
    <li>Contact you about products, services, and promotions.</li>
    <li>Help us prevent fraud and keep our site secure.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Sharing Your Information</h2>
<p>We will never sell your personal information to third parties. We may only disclose your information if we are required to do so by law.</p>

<h2>How We Protect Your Information</h2>
<p>We have implemented security measures to protect your information from access by unauthorized persons and against unlawful processing, accidental loss, destruction, and damage.</p>

<h2>Your Rights</h2>
<p>You have the right to access the personal information we hold about you, and to ask us to update, correct, or delete it.</p>

<h2>Changes to this Policy</h2>
<p>Any changes we make to our Privacy Policy in the future will be posted on this page. Please check back frequently to see any updates or changes to our Privacy Policy.</p>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have any questions, comments, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at flowershop@gmail.com.</p>
